This game is a good one,but I'd like a few more things.Here is the list. 1. White Dwarves. White Dwarves are born when a star like our sun dies. Despite the fact that the game has a White Dwarf glitch,we need that new star. 2. Auto orbit. It's hard to make things orbit in this game so,I want this one. 3. More planet and star info. We need to know the temperature,brightness,density and gravity. Thanks for reading this revew. You don't have to upgrade the game immediately. Bye! I'm out of space.
